# 02 — Database

Ôn **SQL**, **indexing**, **transactions**, **schema design**; đặc biệt **PostgreSQL (queries & transactions)** vì ít dùng trong công việc nhưng hay hỏi khi PV.

## Kiến thức cần cover

- **Chung:** Indexing (B-tree, explain plan), ACID, deadlock, connection pool, migration, repository pattern.
- **MongoDB:** High-throughput schemas cho chat; replica sets (khi cần).
- **MySQL:** Optimization, indexing (BESSFU).
- **PostgreSQL (bù điểm yếu):**
  - **Queries:** SELECT/INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE patterns; JOIN (INNER, LEFT, RIGHT, FULL); subquery vs JOIN; CTE (`WITH`); aggregation (GROUP BY, HAVING); window functions (ROW_NUMBER, RANK, LAG/LEAD); `EXPLAIN` / `EXPLAIN ANALYZE`; index types (B-tree, Hash, GIN/GiST khi cần).
  - **Transactions:** `BEGIN` / `COMMIT` / `ROLLBACK`; `SAVEPOINT` / `ROLLBACK TO`; autocommit; isolation levels (Read Uncommitted, Read Committed, Repeatable Read, Serializable) và hiện tượng (dirty read, non-repeatable read, phantom); locking (`SELECT FOR UPDATE`, `FOR SHARE`, `NOWAIT`/`SKIP LOCKED`); connection pool và transaction boundary (tránh leak, timeout).
  - **Go + PostgreSQL:** `database/sql`, sqlx (named query, struct scan), prepared statement, transaction trong handler.

## Liên hệ CV

- "Database Indexing Management System... reducing average query latency by 30%" — sync index, explain plan.
- "High-throughput database schemas for core chat features... 200,000 users" — schema design, MongoDB/MySQL.
- "Overhauled MySQL... optimizing queries and schema" — BESSFU.

